<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <!--<meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />-->
    <title>Successful Purchase of Spot</title>
    
    <style>
      .body {
        background-color:#DDEBEE;
        color:#424242;
      }
      .highlight-1 {
        color:#008080;
        font-weight:bold
      }
      .highlight-2 {
        color:#004040;
        font-weight:bold
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Dear <%= @user.first_name %> <%= @user.last_name %>, </h1>
    <p> 
      You have successfully reserved a Parkify spot at <span class="highlight-1"><%= @spot.location.location_name %></span>. See Below for more information about your reservation.
    </p>
    <hr/>
    
    <p>
        <span style="font-weight:bold">Spot address: </span><%= @spot.location.location_address %><br/>
        <span style="font-weight:bold">Unique Spot ID: </span><%= @spot.pretty_id %><br/>
        <span style="font-weight:bold">How to find your spot: </span><%= @spot.location.location_address %><br/>
    </p>
    <hr/>
    <p>
        <span style="font-weight:bold">Reservation Duration: </span><%= ((@acceptance.start_time.in_time_zone("Pacific Time (US & Canada)") - @acceptance.end_time.in_time_zone("Pacific Time (US & Canada)"))/18000).floor/2.0 %> hours<br/>
        <span style="font-weight:bold">Time Booked: </span><%= @acceptance.start_time.in_time_zone("Pacific Time (US & Canada)").strftime(%l:%M %p) %> - <%= @acceptance.end_time.in_time_zone("Pacific Time (US & Canada)").strftime(%l:%M %p) %><br/>
        <span style="font-weight:bold"><%= "$%0.2f" % (@acceptance.payment_info.amount_charged / 100.0) %></span>Charged to ************<%= @card.last4 %><br/>
    
        <span class="highlight-2">Time Booked: <br/>
         
    </p>
    <hr/>
    <p>Need Help? Call 1-855-Parkify or visit our site, <a href="http://www.parkify.me">parkify.me</a>.</p>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <p>Thanks for reserving with us and have a great day!</p>
    <p>Respectfully,<br/>-- The Parkify Team</p>
  </body>
</html>